arts.ttl: Eintracht Frankfurt secure UEFA Champions League spot at Freiburg's expense
arts.sum: The final day of the Bundesliga season saw a high-stakes encounter at the Europa-Park Stadion, with both Freiburg and Frankfurt vying for a coveted Champions League spot. Eintracht Frankfurt came from behind in Freiburg on the final day of the 2024/25 Bundesliga season to clinch a UEFA Champions League spot with a 3-1 win.
